0:03:33.160,0:03:33.920
Exactly.

0:03:34.120,0:03:35.320
How dare you!

0:03:37.880,0:03:38.880
Your Highness.

0:03:43.480,0:03:46.020
Your Majesty, the tea can relieve the heat in the Liver.

0:03:47.140,0:03:49.900
Why don't you ask me what I'm angry about?

0:03:50.640,0:03:51.960
When Your Majesty calms down,

0:03:52.060,0:03:53.960
