0:03:54.760,0:03:56.060
Take a look at this.

0:03:57.500,0:03:59.140
Yun-e is so impudent!

0:04:05.980,0:04:08.980
He asks Your Majesty to promote
his mother Consort Dowager Wenxi

0:04:09.440,0:04:11.640
to the rank of Noble Consort Dowager

0:04:12.200,0:04:14.540
and move her tomb to the prior emperor's Consort Mausoleum.

0:04:15.300,0:04:18.700
It is reasonable to grant the prior emperor's 
Consort Dowager Wenxi

0:04:20.140,0:04:23.660
a posthumous promotion although she died young.

0:04:24.540,0:04:27.220
But she didn't have a dignified death.

0:04:28.320,0:04:30.960
