buried in the Consort Mausoleum.

0:04:31.720,0:04:34.900
If Your Majesty approves,

0:04:36.220,0:04:39.060
it will violate the decree of the prior emperor.

0:04:40.180,0:04:42.440
How will Your Majesty be able to be at peace?

0:04:43.000,0:04:46.800
He obviously wants to set me against my filial piety

0:04:47.560,0:04:50.260
and shows no regard to the prestige of
the prior emperor.

0:04:51.000,0:04:52.440
And coincidentally,

0:04:53.000,0:04:54.940
right after Yun-e submitted his memorandum,

0:04:55.520,0:04:58.940
Nian Gengyao proposed that I should
appease the harem

0:04:59.420,0:05:02.220
through granting posthumous titles
and restoring the Consort Mausoleum.

0:05:02.580,0:05:03.840
So Your Majesty suspects ...

0:05:04.680,0:05:08.020
that State Prince Dun is colluding with Nian Gengyao?

0:05:08.920,0:05:10.480
Rice-eating ingrates!

0:05:10.600,0:05:12.220
Your Majesty, calm your anger.

0:05:12.440,0:05:13.780
For the good of your health,

0:05:13.800,0:05:15.580
don't be mad because of them.

0:05:16.140,0:05:18.020
If this is tolerated, what cannot be?

0:05:19.300,0:05:22.640
Even if I would be unfilial to my father

0:05:23.260,0:05:25.960
and turn a blind eye to their collusion,

0:05:26.240,0:05:28.240
how would this make the Empress Dowager feel?

0:05:28.460,0:05:30.980
Also, the title of Noble Consort Dowager
is not appropriate.

0:05:31.680,0:05:34.820
The other lords' mothers have not
been granted this title.

0:05:35.360,0:05:37.920
How can a forsaken consort be the first to receive it?

0:05:38.860,0:05:44.640
If Your Majesty approves, it will create rifts
among both the lords and their mothers.

0:05:46.100,0:05:49.380
It will disturb the peace in both the court and the harem.

0:05:49.840,0:05:51.080
If I approve,

0:05:52.320,0:05:54.460
I will lose support in both the court and the harem.

0:05:54.940,0:05:56.080
But if I don't,

0:05:56.580,0:05:58.320
they will certainly hold a grudge.

0:05:59.420,0:06:02.620
All of our effort to pacify them would have been futile.

0:06:03.640,0:06:05.560
Your Majesty has long endured Nian Gengyao.

0:06:06.560,0:06:08.060
Will you tolerate him again this time?

0:06:08.540,0:06:10.100
Nian Gengyao is allied with many.

0:06:11.160,0:06:12.900
Even if I want to remove him,

0:06:13.760,0:06:16.300
my chance of success now is merely four out of ten.

0:06:17.620,0:06:21.460
Nian Gengyao has been discontent
about me treating Consort Nian coldly.

0:06:22.320,0:06:25.200
He has made moves to get closer to Prince Dun,

0:06:25.900,0:06:29.000
so he can rely on both the throne,
and its aspirants.

0:06:31.300,0:06:33.080
I'm a concubine in the harem

0:06:33.880,0:06:37.660
