Consort Dowager Serein has become a Taoist nun.

0:09:28.560,0:09:30.160
How should Your Majesty treat her case?

0:09:30.280,0:09:32.100
Yunli does not care about these kinds of things.

0:09:32.680,0:09:34.540
Although Nobel Prince Guo doesn’t care,

0:09:34.880,0:09:38.880
I’m afraid some schemers may distort this to 
Your Majesty caring less about Nobel Prince Guo.

0:09:40.040,0:09:43.040
Your Majesty may as well
bestow the honor upon Nobel Prince Guo.

0:09:43.560,0:09:45.320
