0:10:18.340,0:10:22.380
How could you know that your so-called "trivial matters" are not critical ones?

0:10:29.400,0:10:30.720
Your Majesty.

0:10:31.540,0:10:32.800
Peace to Your Majesty.

0:10:33.700,0:10:35.700
I heard His Majesty was incensed.

0:10:36.100,0:10:37.260
So I’m here.

0:10:37.560,0:10:38.380
Yes.

0:10:38.560,0:10:41.140
But Concubine Souire is already inside with His Majesty.

0:10:44.360,0:10:48.380
Please let His Majesty know that I came.

0:10:48.920,0:10:49.820
Yes.

0:10:53.440,0:10:56.100
Your Majesty, we might as well wait
until His Majesty calms down.

0:10:56.320,0:10:57.960
Now that Concubine Souire is with him,

0:10:58.100,0:10:59.980
His Majesty doesn't need me.

0:11:00.920,0:11:02.480
We will visit the Empress Dowager.

0:11:05.580,0:11:07.540
I beg for Your Majesty to extend your favor

0:11:07.660,0:11:09.620
