the Nian family to truly relax.

0:11:30.820,0:11:33.520
If Your Majesty can endure for the sake of the country,

0:11:34.120,0:11:36.000
so can I endure for Your Majesty.

0:11:46.460,0:11:47.540
It will

0:11:48.220,0:11:49.820
be an injustice to you.

0:11:50.200,0:11:51.700
I don't think it’s injustice.

0:11:52.180,0:11:53.620
For Your Majesty,

0:11:53.940,0:11:56.640
I’ll do my utmost to tolerate Consort Nian.

0:11:59.720,0:12:00.800
All right.

0:12:01.960,0:12:04.960
Huan Huan, we lost our child.

0:12:06.260,0:12:07.500
I'm deeply sorry.

0:12:09.060,0:12:10.280
Trust me.

0:12:11.440,0:12:14.760
