0:12:41.620,0:12:44.720
Imperial Mother, do you allow me to confer on her?

0:12:46.840,0:12:48.360
Why wouldn’t I allow?

0:12:48.820,0:12:51.040
The effort is made for the living.

0:12:51.520,0:12:53.380
How can the dead know?

0:12:54.440,0:12:57.220
As long as your decision is good for the state,

0:12:58.220,0:13:00.500
I accept the impact to my honor.

0:13:02.400,0:13:03.920
Thank you, Imperial Mother.

