Seeing Consort Nian,

0:13:10.700,0:13:15.500
I fear that she will become another Wenxi.

0:13:18.080,0:13:20.460
Fortunately, she has no child.

0:13:22.640,0:13:24.720
That’s also the reason why I value Concubine Sourire.

0:13:25.320,0:13:26.700
She lost her child.

0:13:27.880,0:13:29.680
I’ve been feeling guilty about that.

0:13:31.080,0:13:32.760
I know your worries.

