0:14:17.360,0:14:21.660
you and I would not even have a place to reside.

0:14:24.240,0:14:30.480
But recently, you've made her feel neglected.

0:14:31.880,0:14:34.020
Even though State Prince Dun is difficult to deal with,

0:14:34.140,0:14:36.860
Nian Gengyao is the knotty one
 wielding military power.

