Moreover, there has already
been colluding between Nian and Dun.

0:14:41.740,0:14:42.820
Therefore,

0:14:43.740,0:14:46.660
you need to make the effort to appease Consort Nian.

0:14:47.860,0:14:49.640
Not only to comfort her,

0:14:51.260,0:14:53.000
but I also have sympathy for her.

0:14:53.560,0:14:55.920
After all, she has been with me
for all these years

0:14:56.920,0:14:58.820
and treats me with a sincere heart.

0:15:00.720,0:15:03.920
I’m an emperor and a father.

0:15:05.040,0:15:07.320
When Consort Nian was pregnant,

0:15:08.300,0:15:10.560
I had no choice but to kill my own child.

