0:15:41.300,0:15:43.880
In the past, when His Majesty got angry,

0:15:44.680,0:15:47.320
I was the one always by his side.

0:15:47.460,0:15:49.560
Concubine Sourire is only aiding 
His Majesty this one time.

0:15:49.840,0:15:51.480
If the Empress Dowager knows,

0:15:51.680,0:15:53.300
she will advise His Majesty.

0:15:54.500,0:15:55.600
Your Majesty.

