0:32:10.440,0:32:12.820
I heard this from Xiao-Xiazi.

0:32:15.060,0:32:16.420
Did you mishear it?

0:32:16.520,0:32:18.560
Xiao-Xiazi serves His Majesty directly.

0:32:18.640,0:32:20.040
He couldn't be misinformed.

0:32:23.120,0:32:25.720
Meizhuang, why would Sourire do this?

0:32:25.980,0:32:28.480
The gossip spread without any substance.

0:32:28.740,0:32:30.300
Huan'er hates Consort Fluer the most.

0:32:30.300,0:32:31.680
She wouldn't do this.

0:32:31.840,0:32:33.040
But last time,

0:32:33.040,0:32:35.560
Sourire also persuaded His Majesty to see Consort Fleur.

0:32:35.560,0:32:36.540
Enough.

0:32:37.020,0:32:39.460
If Huan'er have something to tell me, she will.

0:32:39.760,0:32:42.120
If she didn't tell me, it didn't happen.

0:32:42.420,0:32:44.960
Let's not let gossip upset us.

0:32:45.600,0:32:48.420
It's time that I should visit Her Majesty.

0:32:48.740,0:32:50.180
I won't keep you then.

0:32:51.840,0:32:53.100
I shall take my leave.

0:33:00.960,0:33:02.180
My Lady,

0:33:02.180,0:33:04.100
Lady An was very assertive and knew all the details.

0:33:04.260,0:33:05.980
I'm afraid this wasn't "wind from an empty cave ".

0:33:06.560,0:33:07.580
I know.

0:33:07.900,0:33:09.860
So I have to ask Huan'er first.

0:33:10.840,0:33:13.820
If she did persuade His Majesty to restore Consort Fleur,

0:33:13.960,0:33:16.040
I will no longer see her as my sister.

0:33:16.680,0:33:20.720
But I think she didn't have to go that far.

0:33:35.080,0:33:36.800
I bow in respect before Your Majesty.

0:33:36.840,0:33:38.400
May peace and grace be with Your Majesty.

0:33:39.100,0:33:40.520
Rise. I need to talk to you.

0:33:40.600,0:33:41.560
I thank Your Majesty.

0:33:41.620,0:33:42.660
You may sit.

0:33:43.760,0:33:47.620
I haven't spoken with you for a long time.

0:33:48.740,0:33:50.860
What have you been busy with recently?

0:33:51.920,0:33:53.460
I have nothing that occupies me,

0:33:53.620,0:33:55.960
just finding ways to pass the time.

0:33:56.420,0:33:57.580
Then tell me

0:33:57.760,0:33:59.760
how you spend your time.

0:34:00.440,0:34:02.660
I will feel refreshed hearing about it.

0:34:04.440,0:34:08.180
The Household Department sent
two cranes to the Imperial Garden.

0:34:08.320,0:34:09.560
They look beautiful.

0:34:10.120,0:34:13.680
Together with the two sika deers in the garden,

0:34:13.920,0:34:17.260
they conceive the scene of
"longevity and long-lasting spring".

0:34:18.980,0:34:20.520
The medicine is so bitter.

0:34:20.640,0:34:22.180
It numbed my tongue.

0:34:25.860,0:34:27.000
Your Majesty.

0:34:32.400,0:34:34.500
Your Majesty, here are some preserved hawthorn fruits.

0:34:34.500,0:34:36.080
Sweet-and-sour will calm the Stomach.

0:34:36.120,0:34:38.520
They are the best after taking medicine.

0:34:40.200,0:34:42.320
You are so filial, as always.

0:34:51.880,0:34:53.200
It tastes good.

0:34:53.460,0:34:55.160
I‘m glad Your Majesty likes it.

0:34:55.280,0:34:57.840
The medicine is extremely bitter.

0:34:57.960,0:35:00.820
Your Majesty may feel sick if you eat 
something too sweet.

0:35:00.880,0:35:03.500
Sweet-and-sour is a more pleasant flavor.

0:35:08.240,0:35:09.580
Concubine Sourire,

0:35:09.680,0:35:11.680
have you recognized your offense?

0:35:14.360,0:35:17.300
Your Majesty, I'm frightened and unaware. 
Please enlighten me.

0:35:17.480,0:35:18.920
How dare you!

0:35:19.840,0:35:22.600
You dared to interfere with state affairs as a concubine.

0:35:22.800,0:35:24.060
Your Majesty, she...

0:35:24.060,0:35:25.440
I asked her.

0:35:25.760,0:35:27.460
Why are you so flustered?

0:35:28.320,0:35:30.720
I don't know why Your Majesty said so.

0:35:31.880,0:35:35.280
But I would never dare to commit such a heinous crime.

0:35:36.480,0:35:38.560
I will allow you to confess.

0:35:39.120,0:35:40.860
How much were you involved

0:35:40.860,0:35:43.060
in the promotion of the Consort Dowagers?

0:35:43.180,0:35:45.040
I believe Your Majesty will make a fair judgment.

0:35:45.100,0:35:48.300
I have always remembered that the harem 
must not interfere with state affairs.

0:35:49.080,0:35:50.820
His Majesty is a wise emperor.

0:35:50.940,0:35:53.180
He had already decided to promote the Consort Dowagers.

0:35:53.440,0:35:55.160
I could never sway His Majesty's decision.

0:35:55.780,0:35:57.080
I was mistaken,

0:35:57.860,0:36:00.300
thinking that promoting the
Consort Dowagers was a family matter,

0:36:00.300,0:36:01.900
so I dared to say a little.

0:36:02.360,0:36:06.100
If affairs of state had been discussed, 
I would never dare to interfere at all.

0:36:06.800,0:36:09.000
Even if you have no intention of being 
involved in state affairs,

0:36:09.960,0:36:14.060
you dare to say you have no 
self-interest in this matter?

0:36:14.600,0:36:16.520
I dare not deceive Your Majesty.

0:36:17.600,0:36:19.420
His Majesty, as the head of state,

0:36:19.440,0:36:22.120
is always worried about state affairs, 
and neglecting to eat and sleep.

0:36:22.440,0:36:25.860
I’m fortunate to be able to serve His Majesty.

0:36:26.760,0:36:28.500
If I have self-interest,

0:36:28.600,0:36:31.720
it is only my hope that His Majesty could live forever in peace

0:36:32.400,0:36:35.340
and that I will be taken care of in my peaceful old age.

0:36:36.500,0:36:40.180
This self-interest, which concubine in the 
harem does not have it?

0:36:42.100,0:36:44.300
All right, you may rise.

0:36:45.200,0:36:46.440
I thank Your Majesty.

0:36:53.240,0:36:56.580
Your self-interest is the same as anyone else's.

0:36:57.240,0:36:59.240
Your lives all depend on the Emperor.

0:36:59.960,0:37:01.460
As long as the Emperor is here,

0:37:01.460,0:37:04.980
all concubines regardless of their status and favor

0:37:05.500,0:37:08.620
will still have a life to look forward to.

0:37:09.520,0:37:11.680
If the Emperor is gone,

0:37:11.880,0:37:13.620
the Empress of course,

0:37:14.500,0:37:16.260
will be the distinguished Empress Dowager.

0:37:17.080,0:37:18.460
And Lady Cao, for instance,

0:37:18.740,0:37:21.300
she at least has a daughter to rely on.

0:37:22.060,0:37:24.980
But childless concubines like you and Meizhuang ...

0:37:27.660,0:37:29.800
Despite your current glories,

0:37:29.880,0:37:31.880
I fear your old age will look bleak.

0:37:32.560,0:37:34.240
To put it bluntly,

0:37:34.480,0:37:36.480
just waiting for death.

0:37:38.200,0:37:42.900
So, the Emperor is the only one 
you can rely on right now.

0:37:46.360,0:37:47.800
The Emperor told me

0:37:50.520,0:37:54.780
that it was your idea to restore Consort Fleur's 
status as soon as possible.

0:37:58.920,0:37:59.780
Yes.

0:38:00.460,0:38:02.000
Was that against your will?

0:38:03.080,0:38:04.400
Your Majesty is wise.

0:38:05.220,0:38:08.420
Your Majesty is aware that someone is plotting against Heaven.

0:38:09.320,0:38:10.760
Though I am dim-witted,

0:38:11.280,0:38:12.960
I understand who Your Majesty refers to.

0:38:14.360,0:38:15.940
Your Majesty has eyes like mirrors —

0:38:16.540,0:38:20.940
in this situation, it is necessary
to calm both the court and the harem.

0:38:21.840,0:38:25.500
I cannot interfere with state affairs 
for the sake of my personal grievances.

0:38:26.760,0:38:28.300
In this matter ...

0:38:28.840,0:38:30.780
someone has to bear the injustice.

0:38:31.400,0:38:33.700
I would rather that person be me.

0:38:37.660,0:38:38.940
Sourire,

0:38:40.480,0:38:42.900
I didn't expect you to have such a heart.

0:38:44.960,0:38:47.080
No wonder the Emperor is partial to you,

0:38:47.080,0:38:49.100
allowing you to accompany him in the Imperial Study.

0:38:50.880,0:38:52.220
I'm flattered, Your Majesty.

0:38:52.220,0:38:53.960
I do not deserve you saying that.

0:38:55.040,0:38:57.600
When the Empress told me that

0:38:57.820,0:39:01.580
you were very conscientious
serving the Emperor in the Imperial Study,

0:39:01.820,0:39:03.640
I was not at ease.

0:39:04.420,0:39:08.100
No concubine is at liberty to enter the Imperial Study.

0:39:08.660,0:39:11.020
And you've always been the smart one.

0:39:11.680,0:39:14.700
If this cleverness is not used in the right way,

0:39:14.700,0:39:16.860
or it blindly leads the Emperor

0:39:16.860,0:39:21.780
to handle state affairs or impose punishments according to your personal interests,

0:39:21.780,0:39:23.760
you will bring disaster to the nation

0:39:24.080,0:39:26.600
and I will not tolerate you.

0:39:27.680,0:39:29.200
I dare not, Your Majesty.

0:39:29.380,0:39:31.180
Do your utmost in serving the Emperor.

0:39:31.980,0:39:34.940
And it will be even better if you can have a child soon.

0:39:35.840,0:39:37.120
I thank Your Majesty.

0:39:40.360,0:39:43.160
Meizhuang has a calm temperament,

0:39:43.160,0:39:45.700
and you have a keen intellect.

0:39:46.200,0:39:48.320
After Empress Première passed,

0:39:48.580,0:39:52.520
the Emperor did not have any concubines truly to his liking.

0:39:54.100,0:39:57.360
If you two can put all your heart into your service,

0:39:57.520,0:40:00.320
the Emperor will have no worries in the harem.

0:40:00.500,0:40:03.380
Your Majesty flatters me immensely.

0:40:07.340,0:40:09.560
It’s time for me to rest,

0:40:09.920,0:40:12.040
so you two go and enjoy the day.

0:40:17.280,0:40:18.740
I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:40:25.620,0:40:26.920
Concubine Sourire,

0:40:30.800,0:40:32.260
There is an old saying:

0:40:32.260,0:40:34.500
"The lack of talent is the virtue in a woman."

0:40:35.040,0:40:36.920
I don’t think it makes sense.

0:40:37.600,0:40:41.300
But being too talented will lead to a hapless fate.

0:40:41.840,0:40:43.300
That would be a shame.

0:40:44.020,0:40:46.480
A talented person knows when to advance and withdraw.

0:40:46.480,0:40:48.300
They cultivate both blessing and wisdom.

0:40:48.380,0:40:49.900
This is really rare.

0:40:50.880,0:40:54.520
In this harem, even though you are just a woman,

0:40:54.800,0:40:57.100
it is a place where a woman’s tears and smiles

0:40:57.100,0:41:00.120
can trigger the changes of "winds and clouds" in the court.

0:41:01.260,0:41:03.000
What you say and do ...

0:41:03.720,0:41:05.020
Be cautious.

0:41:05.980,0:41:06.840
Yes.

0:41:10.200,0:41:11.420
Where’s Meizhuang?

0:41:11.720,0:41:13.480
She took her maid to the kitchen.

0:41:14.000,0:41:16.140
Probably making desserts for Her Majesty.

0:41:17.500,0:41:19.240
I'm afraid she won't be available.

0:41:20.380,0:41:21.720
Let’s go back.

0:41:23.380,0:41:28.840
"Lotuses are harvested south of River Yangtze."

0:41:29.920,0:41:33.080
"How endless their verdant canopy expands!"

0:41:33.160,0:41:34.120
My Lady.

0:41:35.400,0:41:36.340
Speak.

0:41:37.300,0:41:38.400
This afternoon,

0:41:38.700,0:41:41.600
I saw Lady Vertu coming out of the 
Palace of Longevity in anger.

0:41:41.900,0:41:43.940
Concubine Sourire also came out soon after.

0:41:44.400,0:41:46.960
I wonder if Lady Vertu offended the Empress Dowager.

0:41:47.320,0:41:49.600
How could she be angry if 
she offended the Empress Dowager?

0:41:50.980,0:41:54.460
What made her so angry was her knowing that

0:41:54.720,0:41:57.520
it was Concubine Sourire who made 
His Majesty reinstate Consort Fleur.

0:41:57.820,0:42:00.280
When you told her that the other day,

0:42:00.300,0:42:01.900
she refused to believe you, My Lady.

0:42:01.900,0:42:04.080
She was not entirely unconvinced.

0:42:04.480,0:42:07.160
She harbored suspicion and it was confirmed.

0:42:07.960,0:42:11.120
That is why she was incensed.

0:42:11.500,0:42:13.120
I would very much like to see

0:42:13.260,0:42:15.900
whether someone who treats Concubine Sourire like a sister

0:42:16.220,0:42:17.880
will never doubt her sister

0:42:18.400,0:42:20.020
and never develop a rift.

